Class User

java.lang.Object
org.server.User
public class User extends Object
This class contains the information of a User object. One user is a row in the database, and contains the following fields: identifer, first name, last name, riot ID, a HashSet for determining the users that this user has matched with but not the other way around, a HashSet for determining the users that this user has matched with that have also matched with them, and discord ID. Largely null values result in empty String's or empty
invalid reference
